			<CASNumber>66320</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Lithium sulfate is used to treat bipolar disorder and is researched as a potential component of ion conducting glasses. It is also used in applications such as solar panels and the potential for a new class of battery. In 1970, lithium was approved by the United States Food and Drug Administration (FDA) for the treatment of bipolar disorder. It is used to treat mania that is part of bipolar disorder and is also used on a daily basis to reduce the frequency and severity of manic episodes.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">硫酸锂可用于治疗躁郁症，并被研究用作离子导电玻璃的潜在成分。硫酸锂还可用于太阳能电池板等应用，并有可能成为一种新型电池。1970 年，锂被美国食品和药物管理局（FDA）批准用于治疗躁郁症。它可用于治疗躁狂症，而躁狂症是躁狂症的一部分，日常使用也可降低躁狂发作的频率和严重程度。</common:generalComment>
